ttps://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5bc1fe85732482cf.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"250\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-37DD08F3-2D23-4DF2-8BFD-6D4D15B6E6A1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-647CE862-6C90-472A-B47E-3450D024365E\">WHO 보고서</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9737db73-a89f-4b13-baa9-8f39fb3b2c09\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-C0F72CD8-562E-4352-AC4C-16DF274D71CC\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-EA2B70B8-E91F-44BF-93E9-E4FFC82B5BC0\">코로나 치료에 대한 한약(Traditional Chinese Medicine: TCM 이라고 표현됐군요)의 효과를 평가하는 보고서입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24228DF5-375A-467E-9F23-4D9B9723D329\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5BD0BFA9-46B5-4DC5-8716-CD4F64C4F27E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5012387F-A4C9-4C92-8EB9-8A43E8954DDF\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8EFF40C6-2B1F-495F-A305-070C16EA5B0B\">이런 저런 내용이 논의되고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-EBC43A35-014F-49A3-8469-A74B4F94292A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F22E171C-601B-49A3-86A5-486135EF923C\">결론으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da2f8af0-eaee-40df-8632-9c2880a171af\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-da2f8af0-eaee-40df-8632-9c2880a171af\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/105e0ff52c9b387c.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"915\", \"originalHeight\" : \"387\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/105e0ff52c9b387c.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/105e0ff52c9b387c.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"211\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E6712A85-B676-4AFD-86ED-137C73898679\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D9E375B7-F402-4FB1-A14A-67B405F49E2A\">WHO 보고서의 Disccusion 내용</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6ed283f4-c6a7-4bf0-abb9-0a82b7847c22\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51C1E680-AAE1-4CA2-9D44-5FCF877E8871\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E6C5C988-8153-4D82-8EB4-5B0DCC599496\">한약(TCM)은 종래의 항바이러스 치료제(보편적으로 쓰이는 양약들)와 병행해서 사용할때, 안전하고 이득이 된다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6395FD3D-F040-4B54-9CDB-67BFBE5261DB\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0710D7C5-73BF-4E59-9C08-BC20DF312894\">한약(TCM)은 COVID-19 가 경증~중등도에서 악화되는 것을 줄여주는 이득이 있다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-CC8133CB-875A-403B-9D90-8AB532D605AC\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-A0B33B52-082B-47D9-B03A-E32606DC2B19\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1c08cd9-2c3c-4c27-855d-f4620dabbf00\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c1c08cd9-2c3c-4c27-855d-f4620dabbf00\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a4803b5122b526.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"887\", \"originalHeight\" : \"812\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a4803b5122b526.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e4a4803b5122b526.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"457\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b4273d8-51af-47a3-ba50-c481ed65bdf9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-972E3CE3-0C66-431C-8C00-DE15556A8FA7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F29C2DB1-D2D1-4BB8-B0B1-B06E9376FA65\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-111C8929-1DCD-476E-AC47-E5118B16D709\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-B08794FE-9095-4383-A0F7-5082DA422302\">양약 치료만 할 때보다 한약치료를 병행하면 바이러스가 제거되는 시간이 빨라지고, 임상 증상이 좋아지데 걸리는 시간 및 병원에 입원해야 하는 시간이 짧아진다는 내용도 있네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-A00D2992-F387-45D4-AF41-41958664ABE7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2CF510C5-F11F-4A45-BB68-C8061054FEB9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B3B149D0-6D47-4F69-B353-DA973786490A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-C4AC366A-85C4-4363-AC61-6F7D7D02DC2A\">코로나가 시작된지 2년이 지난 시점에서야 이런 보고서가 나온게 아쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-A1EAD5FD-FC7C-46E4-AF52-EAB9F19DC9FB\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F93711A9-A5E2-4027-B4A1-B6C8F953B89B\">한약치료가 효과가 있을까? 라는 의문을 제기하는 분들에게 답이 될 수 있는 보고서가 되겠어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-481122C1-A18A-417B-A8A1-5622A3AAD933\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F30BBBF0-0524-4842-9735-7D8727046AD2\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F9242FF7-B82A-47B6-9538-5C6E7355AFAA\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-A9CEF71D-BDC3-4C08-B776-B85B20D26469\">한약치료 또는 양약과 한약의 병행치료가 코로나 치료에 효과가 좋다는 것은 최근 약국에서의 한약제제 품귀현상에서도 짐작할 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E1D43E5F-00D2-4B49-98ED-C0E0600820A8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-CFFC97B2-F2BF-4871-ABA8-54513524BF35\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4bd01c4a-7b1f-4e56-9de8-e18d04119023\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4bd01c4a-7b1f-4e56-9de8-e18d04119023\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bcf39a9648356ca7.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"569\", \"originalHeight\" : \"168\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bcf39a9648356ca7.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bcf39a9648356ca7.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"147\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f027f103-781f-4f2a-8dcc-e6b95880c200\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7CF9125A-A829-4D87-8F71-32253C914557\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-25E059EE-0BBF-4B23-96A0-B490866B8D3C\"><a href=\"http://www.dailypharm.com/Users/News/NewsView.html?ID&#x3D;286597\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailypharm.com/Users/News/NewsView.html?ID&#x3D;286597</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-image\" id=\"SE-f041177b-f3b9-4ac8-be70-a16602436767\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"http://www.dailypharm.com/Users/News/NewsView.html?ID&#x3D;286597\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22http%3A%2F%2Fpds.dailypharm.com%2Fnews_image%2F202203%2F286597_1.jpg%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\" class=\"se-oglink-thumbnail-resource\" alt=\"\" />\n                                </a>\n                                <a href=\"http://www.dailypharm.com/Users/News/NewsView.html?ID&#x3D;286597\" class=\"se-oglink-info\" target=\"_blank\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-oglink-info-container\">\n                                        <strong class=\"se-oglink-title\">[데일리팜] 한방과립제 감기약도 품절…한약제제 코로나 특수</strong>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-summary\">[데일리팜&#x3D;강혜경 기자] 코로나로 가정 상비의약품 수요가 급증한 가운데 한약제제와 과립제도 유례없는 판매를 보이고 있다. 일반의약품 제제들의 수요와 맞물려 한약제제의 판매가 증가하고 있는 것인데, 여기에 더해 코로나 감염 후 후유증을 보이는 롱코비드 증세로 한약제제나 과립제를 찾는 수요도 늘고 있는 것으로 전해진다. 한약제제를 생산·유통하고 있는 업계 관계자도 이렇게 한약제제가 큰 관심을 받고 ...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">www.dailypharm.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-f041177b-f3b9-4ac8-be70-a16602436767\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"http://www.dailypharm.com/Users/News/NewsView.html?ID&#x3D;286597\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22http%3A%2F%2Fpds.dailypharm.com%2Fnews_image%2F202203%2F286597_1.jpg%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff120\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68fdf400-24a4-41e9-be19-0536f9267286\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-CCD96029-5B8C-4F6E-8532-73C1F5DFD444\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8A09328E-6595-4211-8F29-91E6B0C33FD5\">좀 더 넓게 생각을 해보면,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0CEB5520-318D-4DAF-99C5-B93A826B0A0E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7CA74D56-39EF-4ACC-8B2C-22B50DD1AA10\">코로나에 효과가 있다는 것은 일반 감기 뿐 아니라 다양한 바이러스 질환에 한약 또는 양약과 한약의 병행치료가 도움이 된다고 생각해볼 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4621285F-1905-40A9-A8E3-EF4CBCD7461D\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2ECC6F28-E1C4-4CD2-9E6C-014979743B16\">실제로 임상에서 환자를 치료해보면 다양한 질환에 더 빨리 도 깨끗이 치료되는걸 자주 경험합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-632BE854-B8C4-4FF3-8DAA-BE86248F1B7C\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-881D31EB-6A27-4647-9BFE-45BEEC784A47\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7DF2B996-7AF6-4B30-A208-85B3F21F7375\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-BEC496A6-633F-4399-A294-6FDB6F34CE95\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B170A697-00EA-45F7-AE36-27B7FC26F845\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8770027E-89FE-4AE7-B06A-F664BCBFAC0F\">최근 국내 코로나 환자가 폭발적으로 늘어나면서 코로나 증상으로 고생하는 분들 뿐만 아니라 코로나 후유증으로 힘들어하는 분들도 너무 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7669F58E-74D7-4E76-B89A-4553C0D7871C\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-DCBAC9D9-0477-403F-A21B-02A80EC67779\">코로나 후유증으로 영양주사를 맞으시는 분들도 많고, 한약을 복용하는 분들도 많습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0688DBCD-1941-4770-95BE-91EA84E2B4C3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3FC79040-107D-427C-AE4B-207DBD4EE3DB\">한약 또는 영양주사 + 한약처방으로 코로나 후유증도 벗어날 수 있을거라 생각합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7CF1BC24-C440-4932-B06F-F5DDB34CF54E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75444F4C-5DB9-4067-835E-66ADB44C687C\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b6dffc42-5997-4fb3-8458-d7339289cb8e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b6dffc42-5997-4fb3-8458-d7339289cb8e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5485a66edb645a9a.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"729\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1032\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5485a66edb645a9a.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5485a66edb645a9a.jpg\" dat