  <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ab3d0753-d1cb-45d5-aa34-98dbaf6ba5ae\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bc63b767955e98e4.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1080\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bc63b767955e98e4.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bc63b767955e98e4.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45d1a48b-32d0-4e26-87f5-031fd12093c5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-91253252-17B1-4909-A8EE-F1B55BFDC24E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0AA5268E-6BDF-4F66-8A9B-D3AD623ED60B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4F464878-AE6F-4A7A-88BE-E7379B45357D\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1D876938-4F59-4F32-BD2D-477EE77DEBD0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-D1340590-3F50-42D4-BA1B-382B1D2E6BEE\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F8890594-F003-45E1-A969-65A209B33EE7\">코로나에 안걸리는게 제일 좋겠지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2C5FB53B-20F4-4FD5-9012-5D94002B2BA3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-520FB2A7-B907-4FB2-991B-778654C579F1\">감염되더라도 증상이 경미하게 지나가는게 좋겠죠! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-FFF51BFA-0D39-475C-99A8-07556DEC5772\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9347025C-D79A-4565-A6A6-5EF6746F7DD2\">다 회복된 후에 후유증이 남지 않게, 건강한 몸으로 회복되야 하겠구요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-01AEB4E6-07FE-44C9-B795-5255A63CF03A\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-A04BC7EF-0FEE-4108-98CF-3C62EE2C00F6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-F804A248-25BC-450B-8383-169033C77CE2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7BCDCBD3-54B5-404B-8B25-E90E1B2B75E1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2D661633-76D3-4866-87B3-12BCD6416A50\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D560997C-1667-4C9F-A8F8-0C4DDB062A6B\">이수한의원에서는 코로나 후유증을 치료하고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-95F37760-194D-421F-A2D8-6F56814A7D8F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0F598B60-249A-4284-8018-981C01A15E06\">코로나 후유증을 겪고 계시다면 이수한의원으로 문의하시거나, 가까운 한의원을 방문하길 권합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-EB82994D-6C52-4122-A06E-5B9925E04751\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4469FE31-E382-4C8F-8243-C6C02220719F\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT 